    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>(SN) In nomine domini Dei eterni. Die iovis qui est tercio nonas marcii,
                        presentia bonorum hominum quorum nomina subter leguntur. Per lignum quod in
                        sua tenebat manu <persName
                            key="#childOf #Districtio #Fodrum #Albergaria/gifori #Convenientia"
                                ><name ref="Albertus">Albertus</name></persName>, <rs key="#childOf"
                            >filius</rs> quondam <persName key="#parentOf"><name ref="Rogerius"
                                >Rogerii</name></persName>
                        <rs>vexilliferi</rs>, fecit finem et refutationem in manu domni <persName
                            key="#Monks #Monasteries #Churches"><name ref="Iohannes"
                            >Iohannis</name></persName>, <rs key="#Monks">monachi</rs>
                        <rs key="#Monasteries">monasterii</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Monasteries #Monks #Churches #Convenientia"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/2001">Sancti Benedicti</orgName>, qui videtur
                        morari apud <rs key="#Churches">heclesiam</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Churches" ref="#juridical_persons/2066">Sancti Viti</orgName>
                        de <placeName ref="#places/2475" key="#Churches">Medule</placeName>,
                        nominative de <rs key="#Districtio">districto</rs> atque de <rs
                            key="#Fodrum">fodro</rs> et de <rs key="#Albergaria/gifori"
                            >albergaria</rs> atque de <rs>manducalia</rs> que omnia ab hominibus vel
                        possessionibus predicti monasterii habitantibus in loco Medule petebant vel
                        aliquo modo petere vel exigere poterant. Ita ut omni tempore ipse et sui
                        heredes adversus predictum monasterium vel homines eiusdem monasterii agere
                        vel causare vel exigere non presumant, sed taciti et contenti et [ ... ]
                        omni tempore permaneant. Quod si predictam convenientiam ipse vel sui
                        heredes irrumpere tentaverint, <rs key="#Penalty">viginti libras
                            Mediolanensis monete</rs> nomine pene predicto domno Iohanni monacho vel
                        suis successoribus se prestaturos promiserunt predicta <rs
                            key="#Convenientia">convenientia</rs> firma durante. Actum est hoc in
                        loco Medule, apud heclesiam <orgName key="#Churches"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/2093">Sancti Dalmasii</orgName>. Anno ab
                        incarnatione domini nostri Iesu Christi millesimo centesimo trigesimo primo,
                        inditione nona. Ibi fuerunt: <persName key="#childOf #Witness #Convenientia"
                                ><name ref="Albericus">Albericus</name></persName> filius quondam
                            <persName key="#parentOf #Estate_supervisors"><name ref="Albertus"
                                >Alberti</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Estate_supervisors">canevarii</rs> et <persName key="#Witness"
                                ><name ref="Hugo">Ugo</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness #Convenientia"><name>Amulbertus</name></persName> et
                            <persName key="#childOf #Witness #Convenientia"
                            ><name>Girardus</name></persName> filius <persName key="#parentOf"
                                ><name>Dabiarde</name></persName> et <persName
                            key="#Witness #Convenientia"><name>Teuzo</name></persName> de Brixiano
                        et <persName key="#Witness #Convenientia"><name>Paganus</name></persName> de
                        Perga <rs key="#Witness #Convenientia">testes</rs>. (SN) Ego <persName
                            key="#Writer #Convenientia"><name>Tedaldus</name></persName> rogatus <rs
                            key="#Writer">scripsi</rs>. </ab>
